{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8eea847a-1063-4d7b-9a66-68290aa6f338","content":"The process doesn't exist on this machine (PID 12345), so I can't inspect it directly. But here's how to determine the runtime and configure dumps on **your** system:\n\n## Step 1: Identify the Runtime\n\n```bash\n# Check if CoreCLR is loaded in the process\ngrep -i \"libcoreclr\" /proc/12345/maps\n```\n\n- **If output shows `libcoreclr.so`** → CoreCLR runtime\n- **If no output** → likely NativeAOT\n\nAnother quick check:\n\n```bash\n# NativeAOT binaries are statically linked, no managed DLLs needed\nls -la /proc/12345/exe   # shows the binary path\nfile $(readlink /proc/12345/exe)  # NativeAOT = \"statically linked\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 2: Configure Crash Dumps\n\n### For CoreCLR:\n\nSet environment variables (e.g., in your systemd unit or shell):\n\n```bash\nexport DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1\nexport DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType=4          # 4 = Full heap dump (Triage=1, Mini=2, Heap=3, Full=4)\nexport DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName=/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t\n```\n\nAlso ensure the dump directory exists:\n```bash\nmkdir -p /tmp/dumps\n```\n\n### For NativeAOT:\n\nNativeAOT doesn't use the CoreCLR dump infrastructure. Use the **Linux kernel core dump** mechanism:\n\n```bash\n# Set core dump pattern\necho \"/tmp/dumps/core.%e.%p.%t\" | sudo tee /proc/sys/kernel/core_pattern\n\n# Remove core file size limit for the process\nprlimit --pid 12345 --core=unlimited\n\n# Or for new processes via systemd:\n# LimitCORE=infinity in [Service] section\n```\n\nOptionally install `createdump` or use `dotnet-dump collect` if you need on-demand dumps of a running NativeAOT app (though analysis is more limited than CoreCLR).\n\n---\n\n**TL;DR**: Run `grep libcoreclr /proc/12345/maps`. If it matches, use the `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` env vars. If not (NativeAOT), configure Linux kernel `core_pattern` instead.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7bfdfa9e-8692-42a0-a30f-b8fe3308fc76","outputTokens":591,"requestId":"5020:B7F6F:2A1CAC:348991:69F555EF"},"id":"53068d4c-a6cd-4e76-9897-3e1cdd37ad67","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:40:11.790Z","parentId":"2a4b4069-dbf6-46d7-b3f3-e5695c4329ea"}
